The table presents  the operating revenues and billed  water sales volume for  the years 2014  and 201 3, categorized by customer  class. Key  metrics include a 3 .1% increase  in total operating revenues , driven by growth in  residential (3. 4%), commercial  (5.6%),  and industrial (10 .8%)  segments. Billed water  sales volume decreased by  2. 2% in the  residential segment, but  increased by  1.5% in  the commercial segment  and 7. 3% in the industrial  segment. W astewater revenues and other  revenues also showed growth , with increases of  12.4%  and 9 .1%,  respectively. Overall , the company 's total water  revenues increased by  2.7 %, while unbilled water  services decreased  by 184. 3%.
